<div id="c21">
<p>I heard a similar thought-process called &#8220;FAT&#8221; File-Act-Trash. You take your queue and for each item you <em>have</em> to do one of those three things.</p>

<p class="posted">posted by <a rel="nofollow" href="http://phildhingra.com/">Phil Dhingra</a>
 on January 13, 2010 <a href="#c21" rel="bookmark">#</a></p>
